# Joseph as chief administrator of Egypt — national famine-management plan.
# Phase artifact: rationing-policy (domain fragment). Joseph authorizes the rationing policy for the famine years.
# One admitted PDDL Turtle planning artifact; fragments across all phase
# artifacts merge structurally into ONE combined plan (domain name
# 'joseph-famine' shared by every fragment). Formal planning-to-workflow
# demonstration domain; argues no doctrine, claims no historicity.
@prefix ex: <http://example.org/joseph#> .
@prefix ceng: <urn:chatman:engine#> .

ex:joseph ex:authorizes ex:rationing-policy .

ex:rationing-policy ceng:pddlDomain """
(define (domain joseph-famine)
  (:requirements :strips)
  (:predicates
    (famine-detected ?x)
    (rationing-active ?x))
  (:action activate-rationing-policy
    :parameters (?x)
    :precondition (and (famine-detected ?x))
    :effect (and (rationing-active ?x))))
""" .
